Cybernetic Ninja Rex is a powerful assassin character. Rex is a stealthy, light-weight, martial artist with robotic enhancements. This PBR character model was created via retopology of a high-poly sculpt. The color pallet is configurable in the material settings, and we've include 5 example material instances.
